text: The 2019 Kyrgyzstan Football Super Cup (Kyrgyz: Кыргызстандын футбол Суперкубогу) was the 9th Kyrgyzstan Super Cup match, a football match which will contest between the 2019 Top League and 2019 Kyrgyzstan Cup champion, Dordoi, and 2019 Top League and 2019 Kyrgyzstan Cup runners-up Alay. ==Match details== {| width=92% | |- | | |} ==References== ==External links== * 2019 Kyrgyzstan Super Cup at AFC Super Cup Category:Kyrgyzstan Super Cup
title: 2019 Kyrgyzstan Super Cup
